Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.02,0:00:07.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,0)}{\c&HA0A0A0&}This story is fiction. The names of people,\Nplaces and groups are imaginary.\NObey traffic rules and drive safely.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.27,0:00:16.50,MainStyle,,0100,0000,0310,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord0}INITIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:38.35,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kogoeta machi ni giniro shita kemuri}Silver smoke in a freezing city...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:42.05,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{misugita yume no daisyou}...that's the cost of having an unachievable dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.05,0:00:45.78,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kogoeta karada furikirenai omoi}A frozen body and unforgettable desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.78,0:00:49.45,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{accel funde gomakasu}You deceive yourself by stepping\Non the accelerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:56.81,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Yoru ni kowareta mama shisen tsuyoku togarasete}Although depressed in the night,\Nyour eyes are kept sharply open.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:04.20,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Dareno kimagure kara sekai sae mo owarisoude}You feel like someone's careless\Nact could end the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:06.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,"Break in 2 the nite" It's that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:09.73,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Obieta me wo shite lost in the night}Lost in the night with frightened eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:13.39,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{ochiteku yume ni dakareru}Embraced by a ruined dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:17.15,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kodoku ga kowakute missin' my heart}Scared of loneliness, I'm missing you in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:20.86,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{jibun sae mo kizu tsukete}I almost hurt myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:24.54,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Taoreru kurai ni love me so much}Love me so much and knock me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:28.23,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{subete wo suttee anata wo}If only I can give up everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:31.89,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ai suru koto sae dekitara}...and love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:36.13,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{kitto sunao ni naresou}...I can be my true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:45.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I cleared the corner like...{ DGAAAAAA...}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:52.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was almost like the wind\Nat that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:55.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the mountain passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:58.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When you buy a car,\Nyou should try 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:00.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My car?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.36,0:02:03.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Road Racer's dream, the Eight-Five.\NThe Eight-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:06.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ordinary people wouldn't\Nknow about it though...
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.54,0:02:16.49,MainStyle,,0160,0000,0130,,{\fad(990,990)}{\2a&HFF&}The Challenge from the Superstar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:21.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's summer was so exciting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:24.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:30.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I bought a car, and you swept through\Nthe Road Racing world like a comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you counting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:38.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Four, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the number of battles\Nyou won this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:44.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,First there was the Redsuns'\NTakahashi Keisuke and his FD.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:57.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the Night Kids'\NNakazato and his 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:11.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And the gumtape death match\Nagainst Shoji Shingo's EG6.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:26.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, Mako and Sayuki in\Nthe Sil-Eighty on Usui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:35.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Four wins in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:38.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend of the unbeatable Fujiwara\NTakumi began this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:43.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer just an airheaded kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:49.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep winning, Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:53.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...until I defeat you and become\Nthe fastest in Gunma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:56.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...no, I mean on the Kanto Plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:04:01.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Comet of Akina, Itsuki, so to speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:09.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, we only have an opening\Nceremony today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:11.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so why don't we go somewhere\Nthis afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:16.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I have to work this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:18.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:22.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ride in your car again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...because it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:29.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's cute,\Nit's still my dad's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you want to buy your own car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:34.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you saved enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:39.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saving almost all my money from work,\Nbut there's a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think you will need?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:44.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,About one million yen.\N(~$9500)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,One million, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How much have you saved so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Still way too low.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:05:00.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I gave you 1 million yen,\Nwhat would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:08.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd appreciate it a lot and think\Nthat I'm very important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:13.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you couldn't oppose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:18.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd quit working and\Nlove me so much everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop kidding around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:26.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,One million isn't the kind of money\Nkids like us can earn easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:30.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?  It's just an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:34.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you even dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:37.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:45.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So we know that Takumi's technique\Nworks wherever he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's fast on a course he's never driven...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:49.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:53.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's got good natural senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated all those modern\Nhigh performance machines...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:00.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a 10 year old Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:01.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:04.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:08.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...you said Takumi would be slow because\Nhe had never driven anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:11.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,W...well, if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone thought that.\NTakumi is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:18.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he'd lose when I heard that\Nhe was going to race on Usui...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...against Mako's Sil-Eighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Iketani!\NMy apologies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.27,0:06:30.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I go by lonely driver, Iketani.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:32.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Itsuki's line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:47.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a gas station...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:50.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, these are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,From Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:04.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,From Gunma's number one\Nsuperstar to Takumi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it say?\NLet me read it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:17.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"September 15, 10:00pm.\NAt the peak of Mt. Akina."
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.95,0:07:17.94,MainStyle,,0000,0200,0320,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}{\frz16}September 15, 10:00 pm
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.95,0:07:17.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0190,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}{\frz16}At Mt. Akina's peak
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:22.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's all it says?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:25.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,B...but that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:32.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, Takahashi Ryosuke has sent him\Na challenge for a downhill battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, what'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:40.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the outcome might be,\Nhe should accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:44.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of the Redsuns, his brother, Takahashi\NKeisuke, was defeated by Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:49.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you refuse this rematch, it'll be\Nmore disgraceful than losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you having fun with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:14.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't look very interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You look out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:18.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's nothing new, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:20.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like your mind isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't having fun,\NI'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I am having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:27.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me what you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you unless you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:38.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be difficult for you to understand\Neven if I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:40.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.\NI'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to fight someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:55.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No.  We just call a car race a "battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:57.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Car race...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:04.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you liked\Nthat kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:09.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't intend liking it.\NI was kinda dragged into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:14.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And my next opponent's\Nvery good and famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to help thinking\Nabout it since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:21.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:26.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at driving,\Nso you'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:28.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:31.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like it,\Nwhy don't you ignore him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:34.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:38.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to run away, although\NI don't know if I can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:43.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:47.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to race deep in\Nyour heart, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:53.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You look calm, but at the bottom of your heart,\Nyou absolutely hate to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:57.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike that type of personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:11.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we talk a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:49.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, I know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:54.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...you fought the soccer club senior\Nclassman in the locker room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:11:01.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,After you quit the club, one of\Nthe members quietly told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:06.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You got angry because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't understand\Nyou for such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:19.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.  It doesn't mean anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:31.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Takumi's Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:35.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,W...who's that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:10.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchiya Keiichi's drift is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:14.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at these sequential photos, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:17.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi.\NHey, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:22.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Itsuki?\NIs it lunch time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.\NI'm just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi's been acting strangely\Nfor the past few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:37.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How strange is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's out of it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:41.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not unusual...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:45.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he wasn't that way\Nduring summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:52.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But since school started, he looks\Neven worse than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:55.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's fatigue\Nfrom constant battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:14:03.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was his first experience, so he might've\Nlost tension after school started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:07.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:11.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like he's brainless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:15.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think he can race\Nagainst Takahashi Ryosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:21.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi has a girlfriend, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you ask that so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:28.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought he could be\Nlovesick over a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovesick over a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:31.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You were like that when you were\Nwith Mako, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:39.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji, it's taboo to mention\Nher name here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:43.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...it's alright, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:49.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And I saw Takumi and\Na girl in his Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,IS THAT TRUE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:55.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I only glanced at her,\Nbut she was cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could Takumi's girlfriend be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:13.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder he stopped\Ngoing home with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:17.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That jerk...\NI won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:21.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even been able\Nto touch her hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:24.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!\NThat's the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:30.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drag him out and ask him tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:34.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Road Racers don't need\Ngirls, right, Iketani?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:35.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:39.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lonely drivers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:09.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been going out with Mogi\Nwithout telling me, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:14.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"That?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:19.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it was something\NI had to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No excuses!\NAnswer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:27.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,H...how far have\Nyou gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:32.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How far have you gone\Nwith Mogi?  Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"How far...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're my best friend,\Ntell me honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:39.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki, look ahead, look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:46.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you!\NI'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Last Sunday...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"Last Sunday...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:56.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"T...Two of us..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:58.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...went to Lake Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...Itsuki!\NLook, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:12.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about going from A to B to C!\NYou're really an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"A to B...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:20.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,D...did you kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:21.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,SAY WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:27.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Itsuki, stop!\NSTOP!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It must be because of a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:43.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:44.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:48.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to think so much,\Nbut you've been thinking a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:51.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:57.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He must be preoccupied,\Nrecalling the kiss with Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:03.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm wondering what'll happen in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In the future?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:09.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}After a kiss means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:16.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you say such a dirty thing\Nin front of a lonely driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:19.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what happens after a kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:23.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only {\i1}one{\i0} thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't talking about the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:32.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean by the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.16,0:18:35.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:38.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to think about\Ndifficult matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:43.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I guess his lovesickness can't\Nbe cured so easily.
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.30,0:18:50.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0420,,{\c&HA0A0A0&\fs22}Welcome to touge\N{\fs20}1434m altitude
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:15.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering who that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but that's Keisuke's FD and Kenta's S14.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:20.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta's fast on the downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:23.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His car's grade is Q's with a non-turbo,\Nso his specialty is downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:28.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been recognized by Keisuke,\Nand being trained by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:32.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's being personally taught\Nby our team's number two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a race against the\NNight Kids the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:43.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he should be\Nmessing around with Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:45.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's got time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:49.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So Nakazato Takeshi is going\Nto be out of his league.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been in good\Ncondition lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:56.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think his driving style\Nhas gotten similar to Ryosuke's?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it has.  I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:04.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Ryosuke trusts\NKeisuke completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:08.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he won't show up on Myogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:25.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:28.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you leaving Akina's\NEight-Six alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:33.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you drag him to\NAkagi for a return match?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,To Akagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:36.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:41.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're familiar with the course, so you couldn't\Nbe defeated by a mere Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:44.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:45.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'd lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Akagi's downhill,\NI'd be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:59.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a member of the Redsuns,\Nso you should know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:03.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our policy to defeat opponents\Non their home course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:06.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:11.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...Keisuke, I can't stand the fact\Nthat we lost to the Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:15.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's neither of our home courses,\Nthe conditions will be equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:18.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me...\NLet me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:20.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:26.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:29.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's time to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:33.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a person who'll do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:37.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ryosuke will finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:41.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be hasty.  We have a race\Nwith the Night Kids first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:44.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:07.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with him, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,See?  He confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:13.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:18.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have one week before the battle\Nagainst Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:22.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad.
