Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:50.63,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Yokubou dake ni kararete miushinatteita}...I lost myself to carnal desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:23:05.61,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kimagure na unmei wa mujaki na hitomi ni miserate yuku}Innocent eyes slowly charm my unpredictable fate.
