Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:14.04,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsuyoku tsuyoku kimo wo daite}Strongly, strongly I hold you tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:21.00,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Tatta hitotsu kono omoi wo shinjitsu da to ieru}I can tell that only this feeling is true.
