Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:30.70,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Kagayaku mirai e}...into the bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.41,0:23:52.81,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Ah Kazoekirenai hodo tashikameaou}Let's make it sure over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.81,0:23:58.02,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{Jounetu yo eien e todoke}This passion will be eternal.
