Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.23,0:24:33.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad, bad, really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.89,0:24:35.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}What's so bad, Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.53,0:24:36.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}The battle against Takahashi Ryosuke is soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.88,0:24:38.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No time to think about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.17,0:24:41.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi is lovesick over a girl at\Nan important time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.72,0:24:42.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Lovesick over a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:49.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have done this and that\Nand something really (bleep)!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.20,0:24:52.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Oh, not that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.34,0:24:53.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.23,0:24:54.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0010,,Next time on Initial D:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.03,0:24:59.84,MainStyle,,0190,0000,0216,,Initial
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.03,0:24:59.84,MainStyle,,0000,0420,0160,,Next Time:
